OL,5, Lewis Capaldi has confirmed he will be 
OL,6, extending his break from touring after 
OL,7, a six-month hiatus improved his health.
OL,9,FIn June he announced that he would halt
OL,10,Fhis performing schedule "for the       
OL,11,Fforeseeable future".                   
OL,13,FThe announcement came after the        
OL,14,Fsinger-songwriter struggled with his   
OL,15,Fvoice during a Glastonbury set.        
OL,17,FIn a post on social media, he said he  
OL,18,Fwas working with professionals to help 
OL,19,Fmanage his Tourette's Syndrome and     
OL,20,Fanxiety.                               
